data.description:
Welcome home to this beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bath ranch offering convenient single-story living and loads of style. 
Enter the foyer to a large, open concept living room and dining room with vaulted ceilings and gas fireplace for cozy evenings and large window for loads of natural light.  Freshly painted throughout and no carpet for easy maintenance.
The adjoining kitchen features a breakfast nook, bay window, refreshed cabinets (new doors and drawer fronts to be installed by 4/25) and a new stainless steel stove. 
Dedicated laundry room with custom storage and Murphy folding table for your convenience.  All leading to the attached 2 car garage.
The large primary bedroom is situated separately from the other bedrooms which offers privacy and luxury with coffered ceilings and a nicely appointed ensuite with walk-in shower, custom shelving, and spacious walk-in closet.
2 additional, generous size bedrooms and a full bathroom are on the opposite side of the house.
With just over a 1/4 acre, the private backyard has plenty of room for summertime fun.
Great curb appeal with plenty of parking in the large driveway and attached 2 car, side-entry garage.
All in a quiet, peaceful setting in Hunters Gate community. 
**Sellers offering to contribute to closing**
Fantastic location off Blanchard Rd just minutes to I-20 and 520, for an easy commute to Augusta for dining, shopping, and more.
